title: Parents ignore crying infant chewed by rats
itunes:title: Parents ignore crying infant chewed by rats
description:
A teenaged couple faces felony charges for failing to protect their two-week-old daughter from rats in their Arkansas home. The infant suffered up to 100 rodent bites on her face, body and arms while the young parents slept near the crib, according to police. The baby survived, but the wounds required reconstructive surgery. Nancy Grace and Alan Duke discuss this disturbing case in this episode.
